 FLAGSHIP_EFFECT_DESC: "$concept_flagship$ provides the following effects:\n[GetStaticModifier('flagship_battle_won').GetDesc] from $concept_naval_battle$ won\n[GetStaticModifier('flagship_battle_lost').GetDesc] from $concept_naval_battle$ lost\n[GetStaticModifier('flagship_destroyed').GetDesc] from being destroyed in a $concept_battle$\n[GetStaticModifier('flagship_interest_gain').GetDesc]"
